com.opengamma.strata.basics.market

  • Packages that use com.opengamma.strata.basics.market 
    Package Description
    com.opengamma.strata.basics.market
    Basic types for modelling the market and market data.
    com.opengamma.strata.engine.calculations
    Types used by the calculation engine for performing calculations.
    com.opengamma.strata.engine.marketdata
    Market data containers used by the calculation engine.
    com.opengamma.strata.engine.marketdata.functions
    Contains the MarketDataBuilder interface and its implementations which are used to build the market data used in calculations.
    com.opengamma.strata.engine.marketdata.mapping
    Types for converting market data keys to market data IDs.
    com.opengamma.strata.engine.marketdata.scenarios
    Types that define scenarios which allow perturbations to be applied to market data.
    com.opengamma.strata.examples.marketdata.timeseries  
    com.opengamma.strata.function  
    com.opengamma.strata.function.marketdata.curve
    Market data functions used for building curves and related market data types.
    com.opengamma.strata.function.marketdata.mapping  
    com.opengamma.strata.market.curve
    Definitions of curves.
    com.opengamma.strata.market.curve.config
    Definitions of curve configuration.
    com.opengamma.strata.market.id
    Package containing IDs that identify items of market data.
    com.opengamma.strata.market.key
    Package containing keys that identify items or market data.
    com.opengamma.strata.pricer
    Pricer API.
    com.opengamma.strata.pricer.rate
    Rate pricer API.
